{"tid":180650,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"[村屋] 網上行 vs 和記","createTime":"2017-03-31T05:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T15:55:10.000Z","uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5d8ddaa8d65e92b5844a0fa8b34588aaf21a0c","tid":180650,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"小弟住緊果條村近排好似有和記嘅外判公司話鋪光纖，鋪完會有100/500/1000MB 寬頻<br />\n本身用緊網上行6MB $298，仲貴過和記遲d 1000MB個plan<br />\n所以宜家1516諗緊好唔好轉過去<br />\n轉嘅原因當然係因為價錢同速度<br />\n但又聽聞和記上網出外國ping值高<br />\n<br />\n點揀好? 有無巴打用緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: sales可以過主，附近無其他寬頻覆蓋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd97214fa602de61497777d35eb000bd0722aaca","tid":180650,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"和記印象中係大陸快<br />\nPccw就外國快<br />\nHkbn就香港快<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"fbcdeb16f40c1cfa24f0b0b7cbd18f39bac55f7a","tid":180650,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>和記印象中係大陸快<br />\nPccw就外國快<br />\nHkbn就香港快<br />\n<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n和記=垃圾<br />\n<br />\npccw有自己線出海 聽聞還可以 但係我見啲fd成日爆ping<br />\n<br />\n我自己用緊HKBN 連大陸冇問題 出海都幾穩定 如果想再快啲可以買隻vpn連香港ser<br />\n<br />\n我test過連美國西岸 130ms"},{"pid":"2a309d643b334cc84e69c2d180e562027fa5466d","tid":180650,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T05:37:03.000Z","msg":"平時唔多上大陸網，係咪唔駛諗和記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2030a6eda0d70fd93ab3139db2e4f4dcd729afeb","tid":180650,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時唔多上大陸網，係咪唔駛諗和記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上pccw同hkbn<br />\n邊間平用邊間<br />\n正常一般用途出海分別不大"},{"pid":"7f74f47e03d5305f56ed06ac875af6ec6f3a86c6","tid":180650,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時唔多上大陸網，係咪唔駛諗和記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上pccw同hkbn<br />\n邊間平用邊間<br />\n正常一般用途出海分別不大</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁姐係繼續用番pccw"},{"pid":"20707d2aa38f6c6e7a7be6c0c1fccff1cc10536a","tid":180650,"uid":59947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"有得揀1000M梗係揀1000M，<br />\n和記1000M幾廢都一定好過pccw 6M<br />\n基本上係香港內速度一定足，裝個時一定會同你試埋"},{"pid":"b9d553906cd25e08cf6c40347d4c562240e4ef6d","tid":180650,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時唔多上大陸網，係咪唔駛諗和記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上pccw同hkbn<br />\n邊間平用邊間<br />\n正常一般用途出海分別不大</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁姐係繼續用番pccw</blockquote><br />\n等等, 你講果個繼續用係指PCCW既6M?<br />\n如果得6M就立即轉, 唔好再用6M<br />\n<br />\n另外, 如果其他公司鋪左線去你果到, 你果到既PCCW好大機會都有埋其他速度, 問左先"},{"pid":"be025060c58c60160ab33905deacbc0fd1687d98","tid":180650,"uid":4046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"和記1000M垃圾極都贏6M九條街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cebb276bee8d2c6b88a9e265c6f2c512a76ad0","tid":180650,"uid":10804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"pccw果度最多30mb<br />\n重要29幾加多30 $<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我揾左和記報價 準備轉了"},{"pid":"f5b5bb326a32b932485bb9fe7662dfd7418fc790","tid":180650,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時唔多上大陸網，係咪唔駛諗和記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上pccw同hkbn<br />\n邊間平用邊間<br />\n正常一般用途出海分別不大</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁姐係繼續用番pccw</blockquote><br />\n等等, 你講果個繼續用係指PCCW既6M?<br />\n如果得6M就立即轉, 唔好再用6M<br />\n<br />\n另外, 如果其他公司鋪左線去你果到, 你果到既PCCW好大機會都有埋其他速度, 問左先</blockquote><br />\n網上行果邊之前問過話未有計劃鋪<br />\n<br />\n屋企人唔&quot;gur&quot; pccw獨大好耐，佢地好想轉<br />\n我唯一擔心係出海會延遲<br />\n<br />\n宜家用網上行連台灣ping 50-60左右, 美國連去AT&amp;T 就120左右<br />\n只要唔好差過宜家我收貨架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494fa85296c07b2feda645acd120deb4047edcf9","tid":180650,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>和記1000M垃圾極都贏6M九條街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想打機 ar嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係睇ping值穩陣d"},{"pid":"711f46856fd2d03282c150c604f0394f602670d9","tid":180650,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pccw果度最多30mb<br />\n重要29幾加多30 $<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我揾左和記報價 準備轉了</blockquote><br />\n巴打果邊和記係咩價?<br />\n都係二百幾?"},{"pid":"f6e93cf606b1e222a72d94e6403729f6520ce66b","tid":180650,"uid":10804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>pccw果度最多30mb<br />\n重要29幾加多30 $<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我揾左和記報價 準備轉了</blockquote><br />\n巴打果邊和記係咩價?<br />\n都係二百幾?</blockquote><br />\n我估你都係錦上路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我收到依個<br />\n和記3服務計劃 <br />\n  -免安裝費$1500<br />\n<br />\nPlan: <br />\n簽約24個月送9個月<br />\n100m 月費$258 <br />\n簽約24個月送12個月<br />\n500m 月費$298<br />\n1000m 月費$358<br />\n<br />\n額外服務：（如需要）<br />\n家居電話 月費$35"},{"pid":"78c6757bc0647185480cfc4a161b34eba3a0a829","tid":180650,"uid":53484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"用緊和記1000M個零月<br />\n勁平<br />\n暫時無投訴<br />\n至少打fifa都無咩問題"},{"pid":"62994f82eb6d671b4781cc2ef2ef9b952ae7c13e","tid":180650,"uid":13782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"我條村都見到banner話會鋪,係連登未開之前係高登果邊問過到底100M既pccw好定1000M既和記好,果陣巴打話3出香港好差,又唔穩定,如果都諗住照食pccw算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但近排屋企瘋狂斷線一陣又連番,叫人黎睇又話村屋係咁無計,依家又心郁郁想過檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f52fef8b9adbc26cb594ad6503c74a669526be2","tid":180650,"uid":13116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:13:47.000Z","msg":"我條村都係<br />\n人唔整光纖<br />\npccw死都唔撚整<br />\n人整佢又整<br />\n狗到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想用光纖但又唔順氣佢咁狗<br />\n最仆街係仲有6個月完約<br />\n先叫我加錢轉光纖<br />\n我頂多6個月轉公司<br />\n當係多謝佢出錢鋪光纖<br />\n離左題sor"},{"pid":"64ecbb351e0bbc04b5d52761483159ee6786992c","tid":180650,"uid":10804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊和記1000M個零月<br />\n勁平<br />\n暫時無投訴<br />\n至少打fifa都無咩問題</blockquote><br />\n想問下測速有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35099e397324a20976512bb8e8589e76b9681b86","tid":180650,"uid":58623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"村屋網上爬苦主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成鳩日斷線<br />\n又無得揀焗住用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d651a2119a96373bb49cf50443a713fa1744f0d2","tid":180650,"uid":101463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}